[Amit Varma]: If you enjoyed listening to this episode, check out the show notes, enter rabbit holes

03:43:40.880 --> 03:43:41.880
[Amit Varma]: at will.

03:43:41.880 --> 03:43:46.400
[Amit Varma]: Saaz doesn't seem too active on social media, which is why she's so incredibly productive.

03:43:46.400 --> 03:43:50.600
[Amit Varma]: But you can follow me on Twitter at Amit Verma, A-M-I-T-V-A-R-M-A.

03:43:50.600 --> 03:43:55.560
[Amit Varma]: You can browse past episodes of The Seen and The Unseen at seenunseen.in.

03:43:55.560 --> 03:44:15.640
[Amit Varma]: Thank you for listening.

